==歷史發展==
[[File:Genesis_of_Daic_languages_and_their_relation_with_Austronesians.png|thumb]]
Sagart(2004)認為[[壯侗語族|壯侗語族]]是自[[台灣|台灣]]遷移到中國大陸的[[南島語族|南島語族]]。而之後[[壯侗語族|壯侗語族]]受到[[漢藏語族|漢藏語族]]、[[苗瑤語族|苗瑤語族]]等強烈影響，進而有大量的詞彙借用並在[[語言類型學|語言類型學]]上趨同<ref name="Sagart">http://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/docs/00/09/09/06/PDF/THE_HIGHER_PHYLOGENY_OF_AUSTRONESIAN.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/docs/00/09/09/06/PDF/THE_HIGHER_PHYLOGENY_OF_AUSTRONESIAN.pdf |date=20120223174917 }} Sagart, L. 2004. The higher phylogeny of Austronesian and the position of Tai–Kadai. ''Oceanic Linguistics'' 43.411-440.</ref><ref name="Stratification in the peopling of China: how far does the linguistic evidence match genetics and archaeology?">{{Cite web |url=http://rogerblench.info/Genetics/Geneva%20paper%202004.pdf |title=Stratification in the peopling of China: how far does the linguistic evidence match genetics and archaeology? |access-date=2020-06-29 |archive-date=2021-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411020017/http://www.rogerblench.info/Genetics/Geneva%20paper%202004.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，而在[[漢民族|漢民族]]南遷之後，一大部分壯侗語系民族則又遷往東南亞的山岳地帶。

